# .trivyignore
# CVEs suppressed because no fixed version is available in the Debian 13.4 base image.
# These are OS-level packages in python:3.12-slim, not application dependencies.
# Review and remove each entry once Debian ships a patched version.

# libcap2 — Privilege escalation via TOCTOU race in cap_set_file()
# Not used directly by the Flask app. No fix available from Debian as of 2026-05-07.

# CVE-2026-4878

# ncurses (libncursesw6, libtinfo6, ncurses-base, ncurses-bin)
# Buffer overflow in ncurses. Not used by the app at runtime.
# No fix available from Debian as of 2026-05-07.

# CVE-2025-69720

# systemd (libsystemd0, libudev1)
# Arbitrary code execution via spurious IPC in systemd.
# App does not use systemd or udev. No fix available from Debian as of 2026-05-07.

# CVE-2026-29111

